    "This approach of task decomposition not only improves the efficiency of the search process but also enhances the relevance of the retrieved results by encompassing a diverse range of queries [28].The Finalize agent synthesizes responses from the processing agents to generate, given the initial user query, a coherent final response in Markdown format, as commonly used in other popular solutions like ChatGPT.",
